### Search Tests

### 3. Search for "Christmas" (should find container and items)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=Christmas

### 4. Search for "winter" (should find container and items)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=winter

### 5. Search for "jacket" (should find item)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=jacket

### 6. Search for "red" (should find multiple results - color and scarf)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=red

### 7. Search for "kitchen" (should find container)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=kitchen

### 8. Search for "stainless steel" (should find cooking pot)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=stainless steel

### 9. Multi-word search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=holiday decorations

### 10. Search with special characters (should be handled gracefully)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=pot's & pans!

### 11. Search for non-existent term (should return empty results)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=nonexistentitem12345

### 12. Empty search query (should return 400 error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=

### 13. Missing query parameter (should return 400 error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search

### 14. Search with single character (should work)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=a

### 15. Case-insensitive search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=CHRISTMAS

### 16. Partial word match
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=ornam
